Absence Request and Vacation Schedule Ma.Title: Absence Request and Vacation Schedule Management

Description: This is a migrated version of the Absence Request and Vacation Schedule Management application template for Microsoft Windows SharePoint Services 3.0. The Absence Request and Vacation Schedule Management application template for Windows SharePoint Services 3.0 helps employees manage requests for out of office days. Team members post days they will be unavailable and can use the template to assign their responsibilities to others during those days. The application template helps team leaders manage requests for vacation and provides dashboards showing which users are signed up for the absent team members responsibilities during an absence.
